            <p>CURE is short for Columbus' Ultimate Relationship Exploration.  From our experience, hotel events seem to have these cool, hip, or snappy names and acronyms and we tried our best to come up with our own. We think it's pretty neat and is on point with what we would like to accomplish at this event.</p>
