          Title = "If I purchased a ticket and no longer be able to attend, can I transfer the ticket to someone else?",
          Description = @"
            <p>No. The reason the answer is no, is because a background check is completed on everyone who purchased a ticket. If you give your ticket to someone else, we will not have completed a background check on the person the ticket was transferred to.</p>
